{"id": 3118, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪一刻你会感觉自己的身体所有权不属于自己？", "description": "就，自己的身体好像自己也说了不算。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images ）", "record_count": 1339, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200109213750xSYaj3RmcXC0TUAt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-09T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351748, "content": "领导叫你应酬的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348821}, {"id": 351751, "content": "性交的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011261}, {"id": 351752, "content": "一个人收拾东西，搬家，放东西，再整理，弄完之后感觉累到虚脱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659247}, {"id": 351753, "content": "冥想的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677066}, {"id": 351754, "content": "转牛角尖的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677067}, {"id": 351755, "content": "钻牛角尖的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677067}, {"id": 351757, "content": "上班的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660983}, {"id": 351764, "content": "上数学课的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213106}, {"id": 352532, "content": "死了尸体只能任人摆布", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866877}, {"id": 352024, "content": "失眠熬夜以后", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348188}, {"id": 351771, "content": "深夜 加班完 心悸 感觉不知道什么时候会猝死的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677129}, {"id": 352545, "content": "工作的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689110}, {"id": 351784, "content": "狂吃东西的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506438}, {"id": 352563, "content": "做爱射过之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690552}, {"id": 351796, "content": "没感觉的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677192}, {"id": 352314, "content": "没能打败求  生    欲的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680655}, {"id": 351803, "content": "前天癫痫首次发作 客观笑脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438099}, {"id": 352320, "content": "做某些事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351811, "content": "做梦，梦到很具体的人和事但都和自己无关，醒来怀疑醒来的世界其实是别人的梦境", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646017}, {"id": 351812, "content": "染发/理发/烫发失败的时候，脱发的时候，头发永远不由我控制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223289}, {"id": 352622, "content": "鬼压床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1692998}, {"id": 352625, "content": "你想充满活力的时候身体给你闹肌肉酸疼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693040}, {"id": 352370, "content": "我妈让你穿秋裤时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271727}, {"id": 352371, "content": "我妈让我穿秋裤时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271727}, {"id": 351617, "content": "生病去医院，听医生的做检查、吃药，全程也没人告诉病理", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352641, "content": "不能来姨妈的时候，姨妈就会来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693490}, {"id": 351618, "content": "每天跳操/踩椭圆机，就为了穿得进去年的裤子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351619, "content": "生孩子分娩、母乳喂养", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351620, "content": "每天机械性地做着差不多的日常工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 293, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352388, "content": "姨妈痛！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439290}, {"id": 351621, "content": "在一个很重要的时间段里生病", "image": null, "praise_count": 131, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998837}, {"id": 351622, "content": "大学生期末考试周，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675625}, {"id": 351623, "content": "愤怒的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625938}, {"id": 351624, "content": "胃镜的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676815}, {"id": 351625, "content": "失眠的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373628}, {"id": 351626, "content": "孤独的深夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008716}, {"id": 351628, "content": "情绪失控的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117779}, {"id": 351629, "content": "不得不做一件已知的无意义事项。并且很多年", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519185}, {"id": 351630, "content": "进入手术室里，听着仪器嘀嗒响的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665180}, {"id": 351631, "content": "关键时刻软的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413680}, {"id": 351632, "content": "被催着结婚生小孩的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289571}, {"id": 351633, "content": "社畜被强迫穿各种衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512592}, {"id": 351634, "content": "手、胳膊、腿等各个部位麻了的时候，真感觉不是自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553709}, {"id": 351635, "content": "当面对来来自父母家人的需求的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487944}, {"id": 351636, "content": "“不惜一切代价”的时候，“时刻准备着”的时候，“一刻也不能分割”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278872}, {"id": 351637, "content": "这还用说嘛！作为男性当然是ED和抢跑的时候啦😜别赞💊脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411759}, {"id": 351638, "content": "熬夜到大早上的时候 觉得脸都不是自己的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117612}, {"id": 351639, "content": "超级困，然后又必须硬撑着开会", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729763}, {"id": 352663, "content": "当我不能控制我自己的情绪时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440522}, {"id": 351640, "content": "领导说：你不加班就别干了，相干的人多的是，的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374091}]}